verses.verse: The YY <WH3068> reigneth <WH4427> <WH8804>, he is clothed <WH3847> <WH8804> with majesty <WH1348>; the YY <WH3068> is clothed <WH3847> <WH8804> with strength <WH5797>, wherewith he hath girded <WH247> <WH8694> himself: the world <WH8398> also is stablished <WH3559> <WH8735>, that it cannot be moved <WH4131> <WH8735>.
Thy throne <WH3678> is established <WH3559> <WH8737> of old <WH227>: thou art from everlasting <WH5769>.
